{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# Harness 运行时宿主工程架构\n**Harness = 除大模型之外的一切工程代码**\n感知环境 · 分发工具 · 管理记忆 · 控制预算 · 拦截危险","x":-100,"y":-1520,"width":520,"height":120,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"compact-system","type":"text","text":"# compact/ 三级上下文防爆\n防止大模型\"脑��血\"\n\n**第一级** `microCompact.ts`\n时间断层裁剪 + Cache Edits 无损编辑\n[Old tool result content cleared]\n\n**第二级** `sessionMemoryCompact.ts`\n读取磁盘 SESSION_MEMORY.md\n0 延迟注射，不发额外 API 请求\n`calculateMessagesToKeepIndex` 精准切割\n\n**第三级** `compact.ts` (Legacy)\n单独长调用强制生成 compacted_summary\n核弹级推倒重来\n\n> 详见 [[compact_architecture]]","x":200,"y":-260,"width":380,"height":400,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"hooks-label","type":"text","text":"## 横切关注点：自动化骨架","x":640,"y":-320,"width":320,"height":50,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"phi-title","type":"text","text":"## 三大设计哲学","x":1200,"y":-320,"width":200,"height":50,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"phi-onion","type":"text","text":"# 洋葱模型\n层层包裹大模型\n\n**最内层** query.ts\n→ 直接与 API 对话\n\n**中间层** Tool + compact\n→ 给它手脚，防它脑溢血\n\n**外围层** QueryEngine + Hooks\n→ 管理生命周期与自动化\n\n**最外层** CLI + context\n→ 入口感知与环境注射","x":1160,"y":-260,"width":280,"height":340,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"phi-defense","type":"text","text":"# 防御性设计\n贯穿始终\n\n- 上下文：**三级阶梯防线**\n- 工具：**沙盒+权限+并发安全**\n- 记忆代理：**零信任权限锁死**\n- 外部数据：**长度截断兜底**\n- 预算：**美元+Token 双限**\n- 持久化：**多卡点抗杀死**","x":1160,"y":140,"width":280,"height":260,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"phi-async","type":"text","text":"# 异步影子系统\n并发不阻塞\n\n- 记忆提取 **后台 Fork**\n- Prompt Cache **寄生复用**\n- 后台总结 **用户无感知**\n- 60秒宽限期 **抗 Ctrl+C**\n- 两条独立 Hook 管线\n  互不干扰主线程","x":1160,"y":460,"width":280,"height":260,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"e2e-ref","type":"text","text":"# 端到端流程视角\n另见 [[Claude-Code-Architecture.canvas]]\n七大阶段生命周期时序图\n\n总览文档 → [[end_to_end_workflow]]\n总纲文档 → [[harness_engine_architecture]]","x":-100,"y":-1380,"width":520,"height":120,"color":"0"},
		{"id":"perms-label","type":"text","text":"## 安全 & 扩展基座","x":-1170,"y":-580,"width":240,"height":50,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"permissions","type":"text","text":"# 权限路由引擎\n`permissions/` 安全拦截器\n\n- allow / deny / ask **三级决策**\n- YOLO 模式自动放行 (`-y, --yolo`)\n- `yoloClassifier` 语义风险打分\n  (静态扫描 + 轻量模型推断)\n- `permissionsLoader.ts` 规则加载\n- `permissionRuleParser.ts` 正则匹配\n- `bypassPermissionsKillswitch` 调试越过\n- 绝对高危操作紧急刹车安全网\n\n> 详见 [[permissions_architecture]]","x":-1720,"y":-260,"width":380,"height":360,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"mcp","type":"text","text":"# MCP 协议层\nModel Context Protocol 能力扩展\n\n- STDIO / HTTP SSE **双连接模式**\n- `initialize` 握手获取 capabilities\n- `tools/list` → 原生 Tool 插槽映射\n- Prompts 聚合 & Resources 读取\n- JSON-RPC RequestID 流水线管理\n- 超时容错 & 重连机制\n- 与 Tool.ts 同等公民待遇\n\n> 详见 [[mcp_architecture]]","x":-1530,"y":230,"width":380,"height":300,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"layer-label-1","type":"text","text":"## 最内层：发动机","x":-850,"y":720,"width":220,"height":60,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"layer-label-3","type":"text","text":"## 外围层：底盘 & 生命周期","x":-1170,"y":-830,"width":300,"height":50,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"entry-cli","type":"text","text":"# CLI 入口引导链\n`entrypoints/cli.tsx`\n\n- commander/yargs CLI 解析\n- `preflightChecks.tsx` 探针验证\n  (Node.js 版本 / 执行权限 / 更新检测)\n- Fast-path 短路：`--version` / `daemon`\n- React Ink TUI 渲染宿主初始化\n- 斜杠命令本地拦截，不送大模型\n- 引擎交接 → QueryEngine\n\n> 详见 [[entrypoint_architecture]]","x":-740,"y":-1170,"width":380,"height":340,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"layer-label-4","type":"text","text":"## 最外层：入口 & 感知","x":-1170,"y":-1640,"width":260,"height":50,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"query-engine","type":"text","text":"# QueryEngine.ts 会话总调度室\n底盘 / ECU\n\n- 持有 `mutableMessages` 完整对话数组\n- `submitMessage()` 统一 AsyncGenerator 入口\n- Token 用量统计 / 美元账单累加\n- `maxBudgetUsd` 预算上限斩断\n- `recordTranscript` 多卡点持久化落盘\n- `abortController` 实例级中断钩子\n- 斜杠命令伪装成 AI 回复\n  (`localCommandOutputToSDKAssistantMessage`)\n- 流式事件拆包 → 状态分级拦截\n\n> 详见 [[QueryEngine_architecture]]","x":-310,"y":-700,"width":420,"height":380,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"claude-api","type":"text","text":"# Claude 大模型 API\nAnthropic 云端\n\n唯一的\"大脑\"\n只负责思考和决策\nHarness 一切围绕它服务","x":580,"y":720,"width":280,"height":200,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"entry-context","type":"text","text":"# 世界观注射站\n`context.ts`\n\n- `getGitStatus()` 并发抓 4 条命令\n  (branch / status / log / user.name)\n- 超 2000 字符强制截断防污染\n- `getUserContext()` 注入日期 + CLAUDE.md\n- `getSystemContext()` git状态 + 缓存击穿\n- `memoize` 防止重复扫描\n- 冷启动注射：先喂环境，省一个 RoundTrip\n\n> 详见 [[context_architecture]]","x":270,"y":-1170,"width":380,"height":340,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"prompts-extract","type":"text","text":"# Extract Prompt 提示词\n`extractMemories/prompts.ts`\n\n- **两步走卡片式存储**\n  Turn 1: 并行读所有文件\n  Turn 2: 并行写所有卡片\n- 内容卡片 `.md` (YAML Frontmatter)\n  + `MEMORY.md` 索引条目\n- 反调查指令（禁止 grep/git）\n- Private vs Team Memory 分家\n- 微观路由约束省 API 调用\n\n> 详见 [[extractMemories_prompts_architecture]]","x":-530,"y":1520,"width":380,"height":320,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"mem-label","type":"text","text":"## 双记忆系统：影子工会","x":-1880,"y":1080,"width":280,"height":50,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"prompts-session","type":"text","text":"# Session Prompt 渲染引擎\n`SessionMemory/prompts.ts`\n\n- 强制骨架协议\n  (禁改 # 标题 / 禁碰斜体提示)\n- Token 字数审计\n  (超 12K 自动恐吓压缩指令)\n- `analyzeSectionSizes` 切片计费\n- `truncateSessionMemoryForCompact`\n  断尾求生切肉器\n- 并行 Edit 战术级约束\n- 元幻觉抑制\n- 用户自定义覆写点\n  `~/.claude/session-memory/config/`\n\n> 详见 [[prompts_architecture]]","x":480,"y":1480,"width":380,"height":400,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"hooks","type":"text","text":"# Hooks 系统\nsettings.json 驱动的自动化行为\n\n**生命周期 Hooks**\n- pre-command / post-command\n- `sessionFileAccessHooks.ts` 文件访问\n\n**进程环境 Hooks**\n- `sessionEnvironment.ts`\n- `subprocessEnv.ts` 预处理\n\n**后台触发管线（两条独立管线）**\n- `registerPostSamplingHook` → sessionMemory\n- `handleStopHooks` (stopHooks.ts) → extractMemories\n\n**配置热更新**\n- `applySettingsChange.ts`\n- `changeDetector.ts` / `settingsCache.ts`\n\n> 详见 [[hooks_architecture]]","x":1240,"y":1330,"width":380,"height":460,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"extract-memories","type":"text","text":"# 跨会话持久记忆\n`extractMemories.ts`\n\n**触发方式** `handleStopHooks`（不同管线）\n- `turnsSinceLastExtraction` 节流\n- `hasMemoryWritesSince` 互斥检查\n\n**闭包状态机** `initExtractMemories()`\n- `inProgress` / `pendingContext` 合并逻辑\n- 尾随提取（trailing run）不漏看\n\n**安全约束** `createAutoMemCanUseTool`\n- 允许 Read/Grep/Glob/只读Bash\n- 只能写 `~/.claude/projects/.../memory/`\n\n**Prompt Cache 寄生** 近零成本\n**60秒宽限期** `drainPendingExtraction`\n**反馈** `[X memories saved]` 幽灵消息\n\n> 详见 [[extractMemories_architecture]]","x":-1340,"y":2000,"width":510,"height":500,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"layer-label-2","type":"text","text":"## 中间层：手脚 & 防爆","x":-1050,"y":-400,"width":260,"height":50,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tool-system","type":"text","text":"# Tool.ts 工具插槽系统\n给大模型装上\"手脚\"\n\n- `inputSchema` Zod 参数声明\n- `description()` 供 LLM system prompt 注入\n- `isDestructive()` 破坏性标记\n- `isReadOnly()` / `isConcurrencySafe()`\n- `checkPermissions()` 运行时拦截\n- UI 渲染钩子自描述\n  (ToolUse / Progress / Result / Rejected)\n- `buildTool()` 工厂 Fail-Closed 默认值\n- `backfillObservableInput` 数据反哺\n\n> 详见 [[Tool_architecture]]","x":-740,"y":-170,"width":380,"height":400,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"query-engine-core","type":"text","text":"# query.ts 流式状态机\n发动机 — 直接与 API 对话\n\n- `async function*` 流式生成器\n- `while(true)` 无限状态机循环\n- 流式 Streaming 逐字 yield 给终端渲染\n- tool_use → 工具分发 → tool_result 回填\n- 超 Token 自动续写（无损拼接 8K+）\n- Error Recovery 自愈式韧性设计\n- Fallback Model 降级重试\n- `checkTokenBudget()` 预算追踪\n- 后台子代理 `task-notification` 消费\n\n> 详见 [[query_architecture]]","x":-360,"y":230,"width":380,"height":380,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"session-memory","type":"text","text":"# 会话级临时记忆\n`sessionMemory.ts`\n\n**触发条件** `shouldExtractMemory()`\n- 容量阈值 `hasMetUpdateThreshold`\n- 动作阈值 `hasMetToolCallThreshold`\n- 自然间隙 `!hasToolCallsInLastTurn`\n\n**隔离执行**\n- `createSubagentContext` 环境隔离\n- `runForkedAgent` 派生独立人格\n- `createMemoryFileCanUseTool` 权限锁死\n  → 只能 Edit 一个文件\n\n**挂载方式** `registerPostSamplingHook`\n**产出** → `SESSION_MEMORY.md`\n→ 供 compact 第二级 0 延迟复用\n\n> 详见 [[sessionMemory_architecture]]","x":-200,"y":920,"width":380,"height":500,"color":"5"}
	],
	"edges":[
